<section id="our-story" class="our-story"> 
  <div class="container story-grid">

    <!-- LEFT: copy -->
    <div class="story-copy">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Story</span>
      <h2 class="story-title">
        Built for busy days.<br>
        Designed for clean, steady energy.
      </h2>

      <div class="story-lede">
        We are three brothers who wanted a clean, nutritious energy source
        that fits into our fast-paced lives‚Äîwithout brewing coffee, chugging energy drinks, or cooking a full meal.
      </div>

      <div class="story-columns">
        <p><strong>The problem:</strong> we needed focus that lasts, not jitters or a crash. Most options were either sugary,
          inconvenient, or just didn‚Äôt feel good.</p>
        <p><strong>Our answer:</strong> Buzzbar‚Äîreal ingredients, natural caffeine, L-theanine, and electrolytes.
          A bar you can grab on the run that delivers smooth focus and steady energy.</p>
      </div>

      <ul class="story-highlights">
        <li><span>‚ö°</span> No brewing. No crash. No nonsense.</li>
        <li><span>üåø</span> Plant-based, thoughtful ingredients.</li>
        <li><span>üéì</span> Built for study sessions, meetings, and late-night ideas.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: image placeholder (drop your team photo later) -->
    <aside class="story-visual">
      <!-- Replace src when you have your real team photo -->
